@tinyejp: Thanks for this torrent!

@Everyone else: For all those who have been getting the "insert original disk" error, I figured it out! :D

Here are my FULL instructions (go to step 6 if you've already installed everything):
1. After you download, use daemon tools to mount images.
2. Mount cd1, labeled "rld-sw4a".
3. Use autorun to start installing.
4. Mount cd2 when it asks you to.
5. Just keep following the instructions and keep mounting as it asks you. You have to switch back and forth between the two different disks for it to complete downloading.
6. After it's installed and you've gone through all of the instructions, don't click "play" just yet.
7. Mount image disk1, but don't click "autorun".
8. Click on "Open file folder"
9. At the very top, there should be a folder titled, "Crack". Open.
10. Copy the "Swat 4" Application file.
11. Go to the folder you installed the game. Should be "Program Files" or "Program Files(x86)" unless you changed something...
12. Sierra> SWAT 4> Content> System> paste and overwrite the "Swat 4" Application file.
13. Double click and enjoy. :]
